        <header class="project-header">
            <h1>Shell Shock</h1>
            <p class="status">Currently in Pre-production</p>
        </header>

        <div class="quote">
            "A darkly comedic tale of rivalry and ambition set in a world of competitive snail racing, where the line between human and gastropod becomes increasingly blurred."
            <p class="quote-attribution">— Studio Einfühlung</p>
        </div>

